import React from 'react'
import {  Box, FormControl, Stack, Input } from 'native-base'

export default function Home() {
  return <Box w="90%" maxWidth="300px" marginBottom={'250px'} marginLeft={'100px'} marginRight={'100px'}>
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label>Value A</FormControl.Label>
          <Input />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label>Value B</FormControl.Label>
          <Input />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
    </Box>
}
